_:N6f4d1564465e4e58afeab7ffbd941b6c <http://schema.org/description> "UK Sport (UKSP) supports Britain’s best Olympic and Paralympic sports and athletes, co-ordinating the bids for and staging of major international sporting events in the UK. It invests around £100 million each year in high performance sport. UKSP is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport , supported by 1 public body ." .
